{"tid":1208912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭回應衝突落淚照曝光","createTime":"2019-06-12T10:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:13:50.000Z","uid":4942,"like":7,"dislike":608,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"1a10dc0de01295b5418d661ef2fca8f4cc9fe0d3","tid":1208912,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"政府無視百萬人遊行訴求，強推送中條例拒絕撤回，引發民怨，致今日金鐘佔領再現，警民雙方爆發激烈衝突。無綫今黃昏播放提示，稱將於今晚7時30分於財經資訊台播出專訪，有關訪問片段未正式出街但已流出，有傳林鄭接受《無綫新聞》訪問時堅持仍會硬推惡法，並稱自己沒有賣港，在訪問中一度「扮喊」。傳聞有看過訪問的人判斷，恐怕該訪問會激發更大民怨，抽起擬在下午1時出街的訪問，及後再公佈會播出。特首辦對此事沒有回應。 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭在訪問中指，她的丈夫林兆波指她不會賣港：「我同所有人喺一樣喺呢度（香港）成長，我對呢個地方嘅愛&hellip;令我作出唔少個人犧牲，我本來話講輕鬆，我講輕鬆嗰部分，你知道我屋企有一位不理政事、甚至不理世事嘅老公林先生，佢對於呢個呢兩個字（賣港）都好有意見，但佢嘅講法，就係話，『你點可能賣港呢？但你真係有個問題，你做咗行政長官之後，你就賣咗個身畀香港。』」<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0CyvEJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0CyvEJ.png&h=2dea762a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"023a822aa248fc19e12212dbd4398ce6d9cb38da","tid":1208912,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":337,"score":-333,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2906473/org/5302cff988daa3abd20a459635c06dde.jpg/HVYRobFZ6xzvANZYA4Ofzv_8K_GDLJXfaQHAE2kBwBM?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2906473%2Forg%2F5302cff988daa3abd20a459635c06dde.jpg%2FHVYRobFZ6xzvANZYA4Ofzv_8K_GDLJXfaQHAE2kBwBM%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=06ca2030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2906475/org/2a43cf5fae7128e070dba75765b1eb89.jpg/6kbHg3nmWOFi4BPcApwQKrT-QjPxnB9wD73tXQ-97V0?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2906475%2Forg%2F2a43cf5fae7128e070dba75765b1eb89.jpg%2F6kbHg3nmWOFi4BPcApwQKrT-QjPxnB9wD73tXQ-97V0%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=b689945e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2906474/org/c4926c4088b0913611b4506fada8b949.jpg/k6j1ypC-EEH